        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>New Overages in Crisis Areas Prevention Act or the NO CAP Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits broadband internet access service providers from increasing rates or enforcing data caps or allowances during a major disaster or emergency, including a public health emergency.</p>]]>
